Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:48.49,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}当心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}为你而来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:02.59,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我只想做正确之事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.22,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我并不想称王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:08.14,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:12.48,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我只想拯救你的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.06,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我并不想拿起利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:18.11,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:22.86,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不流泪 不畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.91,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}燃烧 燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.95,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你告诉我 我错过了太多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:32.79,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}仍在浓雾中彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:38.63,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}若我失去一切 坠入深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.55,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我决不会逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:47.80,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}若我失去一切 失去一切 失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.39,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}若我在墙外失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:54.77,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我定将向死而生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:05:00.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我本不愿立于此处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.03,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}当心
